commit.message:
Specify Ruby version by Gemfile and .ruby-version

Gemfile is for Bundler and Heroku.
.ruby-version is for rbenv.

Remove rerun from Gemfile

It seems `rerun -p "**/*.rb" 'bundle exec rackup'` works fine.
We don't have to use rerun via `bundle exec`.

Implement /feed/sources.atom

Using URL for atom:id may not comply with spec as they
can be changed in the future.
But I don't know how to determine proper IRI.

Reference: http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4287#section-4.2.6
Add instruction to install to about.md
Add app.json for "Deploy to Heroku" button

Indicate XHR status by data-status in #result

`.failed`を外す処理がなかったので、一度XHRに失敗するとその後ずっと失敗状態になっていた。
init, loading, failed, succeededは排反なので、classではなくdata-statusという属性にまとめる。

Install bower by dependency

dependencyからインストールするとbowerがキャッシュされる。

Add setting for MongoHQ in production env

Ref: https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/mongohq

Render /about with layout

Add ".container" for bootstrap
Abort last XHR on sending XHR
Consider same two sources as one source

Set #result border color as #ccc

navの枠の色と同じ#7c7c7だと明るすぎる気がする。
Fix the way to check if node exists
